<div class="para" label-module="para">下辖：</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">第八军（李弥、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E5%91%A8%E5%BC%80%E6%88%90">周开成</a>）</div>
<div class="para" label-module="para">第42师（石建中、<a target=_blank href="/item/%E4%BC%8D%E5%AD%90%E6%95%AC">伍子敬</a>）</div>
